    <svcsubproc>
        <title>Windshield- 3 Piece</title>
        <para>The BE bus incorporates a three piece windshield design. The single piece center panel (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f4700654">Fig. 54, Item 1</hotlnk>) allows for full frontal view with no center bar support
            interference. The side panels (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f4700654">Fig. 54, Item 2</hotlnk>) allow for better peripheral vision and rear view mirror
            visibility. The windshield is encapsulated in a single piece rubber type windshield mounting seal. The
            center windshield section may be removed and replaced without removing the side panels.
        </para>
        <figure id="f4700654" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figg47/G4700654.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="288px"
                     scalefitheight="288px"/>
            <caption>Figure 54. 3 Piece Windshield Assembly</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1>1. CENTER WINDSHIELD PANEL</callout1>
                <callout1>2. WINDSHIELD SIDE PANELS</callout1>
                <callout1>3. ONE PIECE WINDSHIELD SEAL</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
    </svcsubproc>
